    "raw_ingredients": "Butane, Isobutane, Propane, Cyclomethicone, Aluminum Chlorohydrate, Isopropyl Palmitate, Persea Gratissima Oil, Octyldodecanol, Charcoal Powder, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Dimethicone, Propylene Carbonate, Dimethiconol, Linalool, Limonene, Citronellol, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Benzyl Alcohol, Parfum.",
